Homepage: https://github.com/D3rPaPaH0d3n/GuardSwitch
Description: Automatic WireGuard tunnel switch
 GuardSwitch turns your WireGuard tunnel off at home and on when away,
 based on network detection (gateway MAC, Wi-Fi SSID, reachable host).
 A tray app shows the current state and lets you pause the automatic
 mode or switch the tunnel manually. The tunnel itself is managed
 through NetworkManager.
